---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ekibimiz">
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<span>PROFESYONEL KADRO</span>
			<h1>Ekibimiz</h1>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="team-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="team-intro">
				<p>Alanında uzman, dinamik ve tecrübeli avukat kadromuzla, her bir dosyaya özveriyle yaklaşıyor; müvekkillerimizin haklarını en üst seviyede savunuyoruz.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="team-grid">
				<div class="team-card">
					<div class="img-wrapper">
						<img src="/images/teammember.jpg" alt="Av. Kartal Yaman" />
					</div>
					<div class="member-info">
						<h3>Av. Kartal Yaman</h3>
						<span class="title">Kurucu Avukat</span>
						<p>Ceza Hukuku ve Şirketler Hukuku alanında 15 yıllık tecrübe.</p>
						<a href="mailto:kartal@kartalyamanhukuk.com" class="email-link">kartal@kartalyamanhukuk.com</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="team-card">
					<div class="img-wrapper">
						<img src="/images/teammember.jpg" alt="Av. Ayşe Yılmaz" />
					</div>
					<div class="member-info">
						<h3>Av. Ayşe Yılmaz</h3>
						<span class="title">Kıdemli Avukat</span>
						<p>İş Hukuku ve Aile Hukuku uyuşmazlıklarında uzman arabulucu.</p>
						<a href="mailto:ayse@kartalyamanhukuk.com" class="email-link">ayse@kartalyamanhukuk.com</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="team-card">
					<div class="img-wrapper">
						<img src="/images/teammember.jpg" alt="Av. Mehmet Demir" />
					</div>
					<div class="member-info">
						<h3>Av. Mehmet Demir</h3>
						<span class="title">Avukat</span>
						<p>Bilişim Hukuku ve İcra-İflas süreçlerinde operasyon yöneticisi.</p>
						<a href="mailto:mehmet@kartalyamanhukuk.com" class="email-link">mehmet@kartalyamanhukuk.com</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.container { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
	
	/* PAGE HEADER (Hakkımızda ile aynı) */
	.page-header { background-color: var(--dark-green); padding: 80px 0; text-align: center; color: var(--white); }
	.page-header span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
	.page-header h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3rem; color: var(--white); }

	/* EKİP LİSTESİ */
	.team-section { padding: 50px 0; background-color: var(--bg-cream); }
	.team-intro { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 60px; text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; }
	
	.team-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 40px;
	}
	
	.team-card {
		background: var(--white);
		border-radius: 4px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}
	.team-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-10px);
		box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
	}
	.img-wrapper {
		width: 100%;
		height: 350px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.img-wrapper img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: top; /* Kafalar kesilmesin */
		transition: transform 0.5s ease;
	}
	.team-card:hover .img-wrapper img {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}
	.member-info {
		padding: 30px;
		text-align: center;
		border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
		transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
	}
	.team-card:hover .member-info {
		border-bottom: 3px solid var(--gold);
	}
	.member-info h3 {
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--dark-green);
		margin-bottom: 5px;
	}
	.member-info .title {
		display: block;
		color: var(--gold);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}
	.member-info p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	.email-link {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--dark-green);
		font-weight: 500;
		text-decoration: underline;
		text-decoration-color: var(--gold);
		text-underline-offset: 4px;
	}
	.email-link:hover {
		color: var(--gold);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-header { padding: 60px 0; }
		.page-header h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
		.img-wrapper { height: 300px; }
	}
</style>